metadata.name: At Crossroads
metadata.description:
In this journey of life, there are moments when we are forced to pause on the way. One such moment is when we reach a crossroad, and have to make choices that define our journey ahead. These moments at these crossroads are when we learn important lessons in life, and the decisions we make,  pave the way to our future. So, always remember to pause, take a breath, and resume the journey in the right direction.

'At Crossroads' is an illustration created using fractal art patterns and represents the decisive moment between our choices on the journey that lies in front of us.

Artist: Dhanya Ajith
Twitter: [@D_Art2021](https://twitter.com/D_Art2021)
